From Diego Aranda Subject Windows Shareware Monthly INFORMATION Windows Shareware Monthly WSM is an on line forum for information about the newest and best Windows and NT shareware freeware WSM is a compilation of submissions from shareware freeware authors in a single Windows Help System All types of software may be submitted for entry in WSM utilities applications games programming tools WSM benefits Windows shareware freeware authors by allowing them to publicize their software releases inform users of updated versions and to increase their installed base of Those searching for specific Windows software will benefit by having a complete list of available software available at their fingertips complete with feature lists current prices and any other relevant Windows software authors may submit entries to Windows Shareware Monthly in the following manner Compose a short summary of the function of the Include all special features which are unique to your product and which set it apart from other programs in the Be sure to include specific details such as the current release version where the software is available how much the registration fee costs how much disk space is required any special requirements sound card or how the author may be contacted Because text is highly compressible the summary may be as long as is necessary however it is best to keep it A good guideline is a single screenful of point text at Order forms and other such addendum may be included if All submissions whould be in plain text ASCII Formatting will be exactly as it is submitted I will simply cut and paste text files into a Help Authoring If you require special formatting conventions such as boldface text or italics or a larger font size indicate so CLEARLY within the text For best results use Windows NotePad to create the Include up to of Windows format bitmap screen shots which display the workings or special features of each Special cases rendering applications for example which require